INSERT INTO `legal_documents` (`id`, `document_type`, `version`, `content`, `is_active`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 'terms_of_service', '1.0', 'By using this app, you agree to the following terms and understand how we handle your information:\n• Cribs Arena is a platform that connects property seekers with property owners/agents. We strive to make finding your next property as easy and secure as possible.\n• Use the platform responsibly — no fraud, scams, or misuse of services. Any attempt to mislead, defraud, or harm other users will result in removal from the platform and possible legal action.\n• Allow us to collect basic info like your name, email, and location. This helps us personalize your experience, connect you with relevant properties, and improve our services.\n• Enable location and notifications so we can provide you with relevant updates on properties and messages. Without these permissions, some features may not work as intended.\n• Trust that your data is safe — we never sell or share your personal information with third parties without your explicit permission. Your privacy is our priority, and we use industry-standard security measures to protect your data.\n• Understand that we may use cookies or third-party services (like analytics, maps, or payment processors) to improve your experience and app performance. These services may collect limited data as described in our Privacy Policy.\n• Be aware that if we make major updates to these terms or our privacy practices, we\'ll notify you so you can review and stay informed. Continued use of the app means you accept any updated terms.\n• If you have any questions or concerns about your data, your rights, or how we use your information, you can always contact our support team for clarification. We are committed to transparency and your peace of mind.', 1, '2025-11-14 13:09:27', '2025-11-14 13:09:27'),
(2, 'privacy_policy', '1.0', 'This Privacy Policy describes how Cribs Arena collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you use our mobile application. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data in an open and transparent manner.\n\n1. **Information We Collect:** We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your name, email address, phone number, and location when you register for an account or use our services. We also collect information automatically when you use the app, such as device information, usage data, and location data (if enabled).\n\n2. **How We Use Your Information:** We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, to personalize your experience, to communicate with you, and for security and fraud prevention. We may also use your information for marketing purposes, but you can opt out at any time.\n\n3. **Sharing Your Information:** We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties without your explicit consent, except as necessary to provide our services (e.g., with property agents you interact with), to comply with legal obligations, or to protect our rights. We may share aggregated or anonymized data that cannot be used to identify you.\n\n4. **Your Choices:** You can review and update your account information at any time. You can also disable location services or notifications through your device settings. You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data.\n\n5. **Security:** We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. However, no internet transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.\n\n6. **Changes to This Policy:** We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy in the app or by other means. Your continued use of the app after such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new policy.\n\n7. **Contact Us:** If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at support@cribsarena.com.', 1, '2025-11-14 13:09:27', '2025-11-14 13:09:27'),
(3, 'agent_terms_of_service', '1.0', 'By using the Cribs Agents platform, you agree to the following terms and understand how we handle your information:\n\n## Platform Overview\n• Cribs Agents is a platform that connects real estate agents with property seekers. We strive to make listing and managing properties as easy and secure as possible.\n\n## Agent Responsibilities\n• Use the platform responsibly — no fraud, scams, or misuse of services. Any attempt to mislead, defraud, or harm other users (property seekers, landlords, or other agents) will result in immediate removal from the platform and possible legal action.\n• Provide accurate and truthful information about properties you list. All property details, including location, price, features, and availability, must be accurate and up-to-date.\n• Maintain professional conduct when interacting with property seekers and other users of the platform. Harassment, discrimination, or unprofessional behavior will not be tolerated.\n• Comply with all applicable local, state, and federal real estate laws and regulations. You are responsible for ensuring your listings and business practices comply with all legal requirements.\n• Respond promptly to inquiries and booking requests from property seekers. Timely communication is essential for maintaining trust and providing excellent service.\n\n## Data and Privacy\n• Allow us to collect basic info like your name, email, location, and professional credentials. This helps us personalize your experience, connect you with relevant leads, and improve our services.\n• Enable location and notifications so we can provide you with relevant updates on leads, bookings, messages, and important platform updates. Without these permissions, some features may not work as intended.\n• Trust that your data is safe — we never sell or share your personal information with third parties without your explicit permission. Your privacy is our priority, and we use industry-standard security measures to protect your data.\n• Understand that we may use cookies or third-party services (like analytics, maps, or payment processors) to improve your experience and app performance. These services may collect limited data as described in our Privacy Policy.\n\n## Fees and Payments\n• Understand that Cribs Agents may charge platform fees or commissions for certain services. All fees will be clearly disclosed before you commit to any service.\n• Maintain accurate payment information and ensure sufficient funds are available for any fees or charges associated with using the platform.\n• Report any billing discrepancies or payment issues promptly to our support team.\n\n## Platform Usage\n• You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the platform for your real estate business activities in accordance with these terms.\n• Do not attempt to circumvent platform security, hack, or exploit any vulnerabilities. Such actions will result in immediate termination of your account and legal action.\n• Do not use the platform to spam, send unsolicited messages, or engage in any form of harassment or unwanted contact with other users.\n\n## Content and Intellectual Property\n• You retain ownership of any content (property listings, photos, descriptions) you upload to the platform.\n• By uploading content, you grant Cribs Agents a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, display, and distribute your content on the platform and in promotional materials.\n• You are responsible for ensuring you have the right to use and share any content you upload, including obtaining necessary permissions for photos, videos, and property information.\n\n## Account Security\n• You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account.\n• Notify us immediately if you suspect any unauthorized access to your account or any security breach.\n• We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that show signs of suspicious activity or violation of these terms.\n\n## Changes to Terms\n• Be aware that if we make major updates to these terms or our privacy practices, we\'ll notify you so you can review and stay informed. Continued use of the platform means you accept any updated terms.\n\n## Termination\n• We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time for violation of these terms, fraudulent activity, or any behavior that harms the platform or its users.\n• You may terminate your account at any time by contacting our support team or using the account deletion features in the app.\n\n## Disclaimers and Limitations\n• Cribs Agents acts as a platform connecting agents with property seekers. We are not a party to any transactions between agents and property seekers, and we are not responsible for the accuracy of property information or the quality of services provided by agents.\n• We do not guarantee that you will receive leads, bookings, or any specific level of business activity through the platform.\n• The platform is provided \"as is\" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.\n\n## Support and Contact\n• If you have any questions or concerns about these terms, your data, your rights, or how we use your information, you can always contact our support team for clarification. We are committed to transparency and your peace of mind.\n• For support, please contact us at support@cribsagents.com or through the in-app support features.', 1, '2026-01-05 15:10:01', '2026-01-05 15:10:01'),
(4, 'agent_privacy_policy', '1.0', 'This Privacy Policy describes how Cribs Agents collects, uses, and discloses your personal information when you use our mobile application and platform as a real estate agent. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data in an open and transparent manner.\n\n## 1. Information We Collect\n\n### Information You Provide\nWe collect information you provide directly to us when you register for an agent account, create listings, or use our services, including:\n- Your name, email address, phone number, and professional credentials\n- Business information, including your agency name, license number, and areas of operation\n- Property listings, including descriptions, photos, pricing, and location information\n- Payment and billing information\n- Communications with property seekers and other users through the platform\n- Profile information, including your bio, experience, and professional background\n\n### Information We Collect Automatically\nWhen you use the platform, we automatically collect certain information, including:\n- Device information (device type, operating system, unique device identifiers)\n- Usage data (pages visited, features used, time spent on the platform)\n- Location data (if enabled, to show you nearby properties and connect you with local leads)\n- Log information (IP address, access times, browser type, referring URLs)\n- Cookies and similar tracking technologies\n\n## 2. How We Use Your Information\n\nWe use the information we collect to:\n- Provide, maintain, and improve our services, including matching you with property seekers and managing your listings\n- Process transactions and send you related information, including booking confirmations and payment receipts\n- Send you technical notices, updates, security alerts, and support messages\n- Respond to your comments, questions, and requests, and provide customer service\n- Communicate with you about products, services, offers, promotions, and events offered by Cribs Agents and others\n- Monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities in connection with our services\n- Detect, investigate, and prevent fraudulent transactions and other illegal activities\n- Personalize and improve your experience on the platform\n- Verify your identity and professional credentials\n- Facilitate communication between you and property seekers\n\n## 3. Sharing Your Information\n\nWe do not sell your personal information. We may share your information in the following circumstances:\n\n### With Property Seekers\n- Your profile information, listings, and contact details (as you choose to make available)\n- Property information you list on the platform\n- Reviews and ratings from property seekers\n\n### With Service Providers\n- We may share information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as payment processing, data analytics, email delivery, hosting services, and customer service\n\n### For Legal Reasons\n- We may disclose information if we believe it is necessary to comply with applicable laws, regulations, legal processes, or government requests\n- To protect the rights, property, or safety of Cribs Agents, our users, or others\n- To enforce our terms of service and other agreements\n\n### Business Transfers\n- If we are involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction\n\n### With Your Consent\n- We may share your information with your consent or at your direction\n\n## 4. Your Choices\n\n### Account Information\nYou can review and update your account information at any time through the app settings.\n\n### Location Services\nYou can enable or disable location services through your device settings. Note that disabling location services may limit certain features of the platform.\n\n### Notifications\nYou can opt out of receiving promotional communications from us by following the instructions in those messages or by adjusting your notification settings in the app.\n\n### Marketing Communications\nYou can opt out of marketing emails by clicking the unsubscribe link in the email or by contacting us directly.\n\n### Data Access and Deletion\nYou have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data. You can do this through the app settings or by contacting our support team.\n\n## 5. Data Security\n\nWe implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction. These measures include:\n- Encryption of sensitive data in transit and at rest\n- Regular security assessments and updates\n- Access controls and authentication procedures\n- Employee training on data protection\n\nHowever, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.\n\n## 6. Data Retention\n\nWe retain your personal information for as long as necessary to provide you with our services and fulfill the purposes described in this policy. We may also retain certain information as required by law or for legitimate business purposes, such as resolving disputes, enforcing our agreements, and preventing fraud.\n\n## 7. Children\'s Privacy\n\nOur services are not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you become aware that a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to delete such information.\n\n## 8. International Data Transfers\n\nYour information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your country of residence. These countries may have data protection laws that differ from those in your country. By using our services, you consent to the transfer of your information to these countries.\n\n## 9. Changes to This Policy\n\nWe may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy in the app, sending you an email notification, or through other means. Your continued use of the platform after such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new policy.\n\n## 10. Your Rights\n\nDepending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including:\n- The right to access your personal information\n- The right to rectify inaccurate information\n- The right to delete your personal information\n- The right to restrict processing of your information\n- The right to data portability\n- The right to object to processing of your information\n\nTo exercise these rights, please contact us through the app or at support@cribsagents.com.\n\n## 11. Contact Us\n\nIf you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:\n- Email: support@cribsagents.com\n- Through the in-app support features\n\nWe are committed to working with you to resolve any concerns you may have about our collection or use of your personal information.', 1, '2026-01-05 15:10:01', '2026-01-05 15:10:01');
